'''海吉拉'''（{{lang-en|Hijra}}；{{lang-hi|हिजड़ा}}；{{lang-ur|ہِجڑا}}；{{lang-bn|হিজড়া}}；{{lang-kn|ಹಿಜಡಾ}}；{{lang-te|హిజ్ర}}；{{lang-or| ହିନ୍ଜଡା}}）是[[南亞|南亞]]地區對[[變性|變性]]者或[[跨性別|跨性別]]人士的稱呼。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://india.blogs.nytimes.com/2013/12/19/the-ties-that-bind-transgendered-communities/|title=The Ties that Bind Transgendered Communities|publisher=The New York Times|accessdate=2014-02-07|first=Mansi|last=Choksi|date=19 December 2013|archive-date=2014-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140109203514/http://india.blogs.nytimes.com/2013/12/19/the-ties-that-bind-transgendered-communities/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://india.angloinfo.com/family/lgbt/|title=Lesbian, Gay, Bisexual and Transgender Communities in India|publisher=Angloinfo; the Global Expat Network INDIA|accessdate=2014-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140220100029/http://india.angloinfo.com/family/lgbt/|archive-date=2014-02-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>海吉拉通常被认为是[[第三性|第三性]]的一个成员——既不是男人，也不是女人。绝大多数的海吉拉都是生理男性或者[[双性人|双性人]]，但也有部分生理女性的海吉拉（一般被称为'''海吉拉斯'''）。
